Fun facts about me 👱🏼‍♀️😱 
Datos divertidos sobre mí, que opinan?

1- My grandfather Rauldel, was a bull fighter

2- My grandmother Tomasa, gave birth to Raudel 21 children. 

3- My name comes from a radio soap opera that was once broadcasted on the air. Olga Lidia was the name of the villain. Who eventually died from quicksand lol. 

4- My favorite food is tacos and sushi. But never together.. of course 

5- My favorite sweats is mango
con chili. 

6- The one food that is absolutely disgusting to me is mint chocolate. Yuk!! 

7- I’m allergic to blue berries 

8- I collect coins. Known as numismatist

9- My biggest fear is to be stuck in the forest alone. Yikes. 

10- I own 40 pairs of pajamas but don’t wear anything to bed
